captions.text: that this video hits a snag
you get a little buffer action
how long are you willing to wait?
sign up again and confirm your age
burrito that you dropped on the beach one time
and you got a little hunger pain you see
so you head down the hall to find the vending machine
that's where the snack that you like resides
but when you press F-14 the coil gets stuck
and your snack is still inside
so now you gotta start shaking the machine
how long are you going to shake this machine
until you begin to eat away at your own dignity?
carrots, hummus, and grapes in a bunch
It's just a bag of Fritos
do you really need those Fritos
that pepperoni pizza on a Walgreen's parking lot
So you find yourself on a date with a beautiful girl
you try to tell her all the things that interest you in the world
she said she doesn't like wizards
she said she doesn't like lizards
you try to stay quiet like it aint no thing
but how long can you let that silence hang?
on the errant hair on her face
you think of somethin' to say
just wait for the silence to go away
protein shake on a locker room floor
How long do you wait when you reset the internet router?
How long do wait before you give up on the hot water in the shower?
when you drop some food on the ceiling?
well how long can you hold your breath
before you get that oh I'm dyin' feeling?
claim a fart in a group
give up on a fish that's floating
to decide this small little pond is not suitable for boating
trail mix literally on the trail
